TI  - Prevalence of mutations in the Plasmodium falciparum chloroquine resistance transporter, PfCRT, and association with ex vivo susceptibility to common anti-malarial drugs against African Plasmodium falciparum isolates
AU  - Foguim, FT
AU  - Bogreau, H
AU  - Gendrot, M
AU  - Mosnier, J
AU  - Fonta, I
