TI  - Genetic mutations in pfcrt and pfmdr1 at the time of artemisinin combination therapy introduction in South Pacific islands of Vanuatu and Solomon Islands
AU  - Gresty, KJ
AU  - Gray, KA
AU  - Bobogare, A
AU  - Taleo, G
AU  - Hii, J
AU  - Wini, L
AU  - Cheng, Q
