TI  - A novel Modulator of Ring Stage Translation (MRST) gene alters artemisinin sensitivity in Plasmodium falciparum
AU  - Simmons, C
AU  - Gibbons, J
AU  - Wang, CQ
AU  - Pires, CV
AU  - Zhang, M
