TI  - Emergence of artemisinin-based combination treatment failure in patients returning from sub-Saharan Africa with P. falciparum malaria
AU  - Grossman, T
AU  - Vainer, J
AU  - Paran, Y
AU  - Studentsky, L
AU  - Manor, U
