TI  - Effectiveness of sulfadoxine-pyrimethamine plus amodiaquine and dihydroartemisinin-piperaquine for seasonal malaria chemoprevention in Uganda: a three-arm, open-label, non-inferiority and superiority, cluster-randomised, controlled trial
